<div class="blog_posting_title_large"><h2>Smart fryer uses a mere tablespoon of olive oil to make chips</h2></div>






<div class="permalink_post_content">

<div id="permalinks_share">





<div class="social_badge" style="margin-bottom:10px">
<script type="text/javascript">
